E. L. POWELL & SONS TRUCKING CO., a copartnership composed of, and Herbert H. Powell and Ben L. Powell, who are also the surviving partners, v. RAYMOND CONCRETE PILE COMPANY, a corporation, and Raymond International, Inc., a corporation. No. 6318. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Sept. 14, 1960. Milton W. Hardy, Tulsa, Okl., for appellants. Holleman & Holleman, Tulsa, Old., for appellees.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, and BRATTON and PICKETT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed pursuant to stipulation.
